downloadTitle: Skype for Business Server 2019, Debugging Tools
downloadDescription: Skype for Business Server 2019, Debugging Tools are provided to help IT Administrators with troubleshooting deployments of Skype for Business Server 2019.
detailsSection:
Skype for Business Server 2019, Debugging Tools is a collection of additional tools for use by IT Admins to aid in troubleshooting Skype for Business Server 2019 deployments. The collection of tools include:
  • Snooper
  • CLSLogger
  • CLSScenarioEdit.psm1
systemRequirementsSection: Please see Skype for Business Server 2019 System Requirements
installInstructionSection:
Please note, if you have a higher version installed previously, you need to un-install it first and re-install.
To install this download
  1. Download the file by clicking the Download button and saving the file to your hard disk.
  2. Browse to the location you downloaded the file and run the SkypeforBusinessDebgTools.msi.
  3. The installation will drop the files (by default) to C:\Program Files\Skype for Business Server 2019\Debugging Tools. Browse to this directory to find the tools.


To uninstall this download
  1. Click the Start button, and then select Control Panel.
  2. Click Uninstall a program from the Programs item.
  3. Right click Skype for Business Server, Debugging Tools to select Uninstall.
  4. Follow the wizard to finish uninstalling this download.
